data.description: In the quiet community of Barefoot Bay This is a lifestyle Lots of activities at the Club House, Beach access, Pier to fish, So many clubs to join 3 pools, Golf Close to stores & restaurants, two A/C, one for the home & one for large closed in porch, Main Ac has been serviced & all new ducts Roof is new! There is a large room off back great for storage or workshop Very large Front living room Has a family room 2 baths large master bed across back of home. Large open kitchen with Island, and Laundry inside.. all freshly painted & You own the lot! A must see!
